long.et,fa,hr,id,ko,nl,no,sv:
Ad Blocker is a powerful yet light-weight solution for removing all types of Ads from all websites. Ad Blocker was designed to create and maintain a comfortable and safe Internet surfing by blocking annoying ads and dangerous activities of websites. We block:
-	Banner ads
-	Chat windows
-	Video ads
-	Pop-ups and pop-unders

Using Ad Blocker gives a range of advantages of ads-free Internet as well as makes user experience smooth and safe. For this Ad Blocker:
-	Removes annoying ads
-	Blocks malicious redirects
-	Blocks data mining and collection while protecting your personal information
-	Speeds up your Browser operation by removing unneeded advertising processes

This AdBlocker works not only on all regular websites but also on most popular social networks, video and streaming platforms like:
-	YouTube
-	Twitch
-	Instagram
-	Twitter
and many more.

Ad Blocker is a very simple tool, all you need is to add it to your Chrome and that's it. Enjoy safe and smooth user experience.
